	<article class="post-81705 post type-post status-publish hentry category-dashboard tag-entrepreneurship tag-new-jersey tag-small-business tag-start-ups des-entrepreneurship des-small-business des-start-ups geo-new-jersey" id="post-81705">
	<header class="postHeader">
				<div class="postKicker">
					</div>
				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Today in Small Business: Learning From the Big Sites</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Gene Marks			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-01-13T17:18:28+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">January 13, 2014 12:18 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">January 13, 2014 12:18 pm</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content"><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>The Economy</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Here is <a href="//www.npr.org/blogs/money/2014/01/09/261053608/every-job-in-america-in-1-graph?">every job</a> in America in one infographic.</li>
<li>Jared Bernstein <a href="//jaredbernsteinblog.com/will-the-real-unemployment-rate-please-stand-up/">wants to know</a> what the real unemployment rate is.</li>
<li>Bill McBride predicts that <a href="//www.calculatedriskblog.com/2014/01/update-when-will-payroll-employment.html?">payroll levels will exceed</a> their pre-recession peak by the middle of the year.</li>
<li>The forecast for global <a href="//www.brecorder.com/business-a-economy/189:pakistan/1143240:global-auto-sales-forecast-rosy-with-reservations-for-2014/">auto sales</a> is rosy (with reservations), and technology <a href="//www.usatoday.com/story/tech/columnist/shinal/2014/01/12/tech-earnings-preview-new-tech-economy-john-shinal/4391789/">profits are expected</a> to surge.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Start-Up</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>How one entrepreneur figured out what <a href="//www.washingtonpost.com/business/on-small-business/a-new-vision-how-one-entrepreneur-changed-his-thinking-about-the-blind/2014/01/10/25b615a4-794d-11e3-af7f-13bf0e9965f6_story.html">blind watch-buyers</a> really wanted.</li>
<li>The Story Exchange is looking for <a href="//thestoryexchange.org/feature-startup-story/">women business owners from around the world</a> who want to tell their start-up stories.</li>
<li>And here are some pointers on how to <a href="//firstround.com/article/The-Seven-Deadly-Sins-of-Startup-Storytelling?utm_content=buffer0fe88&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter.com&amp;utm_campaign=buffer">tell that story</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span id="more-81705"></span><b>Online</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Here are three things <a href="//www.solopreneursllc.com/3-main-things-you-can-learn-from-top-e-commerce-sites/?">you can learn</a> from the big e-commerce sites.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Management</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Ken Keller explains why it&#8217;s important to <a href="//www.signalscv.com/section/25/article/112202/">get rid of</a> toxic employees: âThese employees are expensive; they not only receive a paycheck, but they are typically disengaged, under-performing, high-maintenance, and require additional supervisory time to keep them on track.â</li>
<li>How a New Jersey bowling alley <a href="//www.nj.com/cumberland/index.ssf/2014/01/man_accused_in_vineland_bowling_alley_arson.html">dealt with a competitor</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Finance</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Hereâs why <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/01/12/us/banks-say-no-to-marijuana-money-legal-or-not.html">banks arenât accepting legal marijuana</a> money.</li>
<li>Bank of America says it will <a href="//www.nydailynews.com/news/national/bank-america-improve-intern-working-conditions-article-1.1576425">improve working conditions</a> for junior bankers after the death of a summer intern.</li>
<li>Bitcoin ATMs <a href="//nypost.com/2014/01/12/first-bitcoin-atm-to-debut-in-nyc/">are coming</a> to New York City.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Sales and Marketing</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Matt Hodkinson offers advice for <a href="//www.influenceagents.com/matts-chat/when-leads-dont-just-happen">getting leads.</a></li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Around the Country</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Here are the 10 <a href="//247wallst.com/special-report/2014/01/10/the-10-most-hated-companies-in-america-3/">most-hated</a> companies in America.</li>
<li>A Northern California woman <a href="//www.pressdemocrat.com/article/20140112/business/140119947">becomes the first resident entrepreneur</a> of the United Nations Foundation, a Washington-based nonprofit that Ted Turner started.</li>
<li>A Montana entrepreneur creates <a href="//mtstandard.com/news/local/the-right-track-local-entrepreneur-creates--of-a-kind/article_a57143ac-7b3e-11e3-a06b-001a4bcf887a.html">one-of-a-kind tools</a> for NASA.</li>
<li>A panel says New Hampshire <a href="//www.unionleader.com/article/20140112/NEWS02/140119880">needs more</a> women-owned businesses.</li>
<li>A utility service in Mississippi says it has helped more than <a href="//www.desototimes.com/articles/2014/01/12/news/local/doc52d09c49c5304429771832.txt">1,100 small businesses</a> save more than $400,000 in start-up costs.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Around the World</b></p>
<ul>
<li>Sunday was the 13th annual worldwide <a href="//mentalfloss.com/article/54494/today-13th-annual-no-pants-subway-ride">no-pants subway ride</a> day.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Health Care</b></p>
<ul>
<li>In October, <a href="//www.washingtonpost.com/national/health-science/second-wave-of-health-insurance-disruption-affects-small-businesses/2014/01/11/dc2f7404-6ffe-11e3-a523-fe73f0ff6b8d_story.html">millions of people</a> who receive insurance through small employers may be disrupted by cancellations.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Technology</b></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="//www.chicagotribune.com/business/breaking/chi-target-data-breach-affected-70-million-customers-20140110,0,621285.story">Target</a> reports more customer data breaches, and <a href="//krebsonsecurity.com/2014/01/hackers-steal-card-data-from-neiman-marcus/">Neiman Marcus</a> gets hacked, too.</li>
<li>A Portland, Ore. companyâs drone technology <a href="//www.statesmanjournal.com/article/20140112/BUSINESS01/301120007?">could transform agriculture</a>, and a United Kingdom <a href="//metro.co.uk/2014/01/12/school-invests-in-drone-technology-to-patrol-exam-halls-and-stop-cheats-4259385/">school invests</a> in drone technology to patrol exam halls and stop cheats.</li>
</ul>
